       <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=19914&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=6054&amp;mobile=yes" rel="nofollow" class="xg1">只看他</a> 
       <br />
       <em id="authorposton308603"><font class="xs0 xg1">2006-11-16 10:46</font></em> 
      </div> 
