       <sup>#</sup> 
       <a href="home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=9176&amp;mobile=yes" target="_blank">无聊69</a> 
       <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=19914&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=9176&amp;mobile=yes" rel="nofollow" class="xg1">只看他</a> 
